<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>دخول - محفظة المفيد نت</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Tahoma', sans-serif; }
        body { background: linear-gradient(145deg, #0b1120, #19233c); min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 20px; }
        .login-card { background: rgba(18, 28, 45, 0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); padding: 40px; border-radius: 30px; border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3); width: 100%; max-width: 400px; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
        .login-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -50%; left: -50%; width: 200%; height: 200%; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%); z-index: 0; }
        .content-wrapper { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
        .logo { font-size: 50px; margin-bottom: 20px; display: inline-block; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3)); }
        .title { color: #d4af37; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .date-badge { background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1); color: #d4af37; padding: 5px 15px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 12px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 25px; border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2); }
        .error-msg { background: rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.1); color: #ff4d4d; padding: 12px; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 14px; border: 1px solid rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.2); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px; }
        .input-group { margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: right; }
        .input-label { display: block; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 14px; margin-right: 5px; }
        .input-field { width: 100%; padding: 15px; border-radius: 15px; border: 1px solid #2a3a5a; background: #0b1120; color: white; font-size: 16px; transition: all 0.3s ease; text-align: center; }
        .input-field:focus { border-color: #d4af37; outline: none; box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1); background: #0f1a2f; }
        .login-btn { width: 100%; padding: 15px; border-radius: 15px; border: none; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4af37, #b48c2c); color: #0b1120; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s ease; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(180, 140, 44, 0.3); margin-top: 10px; }
        .login-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2); }
        .login-btn:active { transform: translateY(-1px); }
        .help-links { margin-top: 25px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 15px; }
        .help-link { color: #aaa; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px; transition: 0.3s; }
        .help-link:hover { color: #d4af37; }
        .dev-section { margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #2a3a5a; }
        .dev-title { color: #666; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 15px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .dev-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; }
        .dev-item { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); padding: 10px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); }
        .dev-name { color: #d4af37; font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 4px; }
        .dev-phone { color: #444; font-size: 10px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; }
        .footer-note { margin-top: 20px; color: #333; font-size: 10px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="login-card">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <div class="logo">📱</div>
            <h1 class="title">محفظة المفيد نت</h1>
            <div class="date-badge">🗓 <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('ar-YE') %></div>
            
            <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 30px;">أهلاً بك، سجل دخولك للمتابعة</p>

            <% if (error) { %>
                <div class="error-msg"><%= error %></div>
            <% } %>

            <form action="/login" method="POST">
                <div class="input-group">
                    <label class="input-label">رقم الهاتف</label>
                    <div style="position: relative;">
                        <input type="text" name="phone" class="input-field" placeholder="أدخل رقم الهاتف" required>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="input-group">
                    <label class="input-label">كلمة المرور</label>
                    <div style="position: relative;">
                        <input type="password" name="password" class="input-field" placeholder="أدخل كلمة المرور" required>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <button type="submit" class="login-btn">دخول</button>
            </form>
            
            <div class="help-links">
                <a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=967736136681&text=السلام عليكم، نسيت كلمة المرور" class="help-link" target="_blank">
                    <span>🔐</span> نسيت كلمة المرور؟
                </a>
                <a href="/register" class="help-link">
                    <span>✨</span> مستخدم جديد؟
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="dev-section">
                <div class="dev-title">✨ برمجة وتطوير ✨</div>
                <div class="dev-grid">
                    <div class="dev-item">
                        <div class="dev-name">Wheeb Asaaj</div>
                        <div class="dev-phone">773368764</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="dev-item">
                        <div class="dev-name">Abo Al-Hassan</div>
                        <div class="dev-phone">736136681</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer-note">
                جميع الحقوق محفوظة © 2026
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
